    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[13]'
      value: You can upgrade a Grabber into a Smart Grabber. A Smart Grabber lets
        you choose which item it will pick up.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[14]'
      value: "Trust me, you\u2019ll need a smarter machine to avoid picking up unprocessed
        dough by mistake"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[15]'
